                <head>172. Summary of Conclusions of a Special Coordination Committee Meeting<note
                        n="1" type="source" xml:id="d172fn1">Source: Carter Library, National
                        Security Affairs, Staff Material, Middle East File, Box 99, Meetings File,
                        1/30 and 31/80 <gloss target="#t_SCC_1">SCC</gloss> re Iran. Top Secret. The
